T*
(- Algorithms: The main topic being studied, understood here as algorithms are logical) Tj
T*
(step-by-step procedures for solving problems.) Tj
T*
(- Core Focus: The main idea the learner must understand in this lesson: clear) Tj
T*
(instructions, efficiency, and correctness.) Tj
T*
(- Application: The point where the explanation is used in practice, such as writing an) Tj
T*
(algorithm to sort items or search a list.) Tj
T*
(- Common Error: A repeated learner difficulty in this topic, for example leaving steps) Tj
T*
(ambiguous or unordered.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
