T*
(- Misunderstanding the core focus of Algorithms: clear instructions, efficiency, and) Tj
T*
(correctness.) Tj
T*
(- Leaving steps ambiguous or unordered.) Tj
T*
(- Jumping to an answer without showing the steps or reasoning clearly.) Tj
T*
