(Summary) Tj
T*
(Algorithms is a valuable part of Computer Science. Students perform better when they) Tj
T*
(understand clear instructions, efficiency, and correctness, learn from examples such as) Tj
T*
(writing an algorithm to sort items or search a list, and deliberately avoid mistakes) Tj
T*
(like leaving steps ambiguous or unordered. Regular practice built around algorithm) Tj
T*
(design and tracing makes the topic easier to remember and apply.) Tj
